{"tid":2368403,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"議長佩洛西說有共和黨議員拒絕配合安檢，出言侮辱國會警察，計劃向不合作的議員罰款，從議員薪金扣取五千美元，再犯扣一萬。","createTime":"2021-01-16T06:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T07:58:41.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fd45f1eeb655e3adee2fed9a7dc33750f590e07b","tid":2368403,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T06:59:47.000Z","msg":"因應下周總統就職典禮，美國國會大廈一帶加強戒備，華盛頓將增派國民警衛隊至二萬人。聯邦調查局等負責就職典禮保安的部門，已經向拜登團隊簡介安排。<br />\n<br />\n在眾議員辯論彈劾議案的同一日，數以百計國民警衛隊進駐眾議院大廳戒備，是1860年代南北戰爭以來再次有軍人進駐國會大廈，部分人配備長槍。<br />\n<br />\n國民警衛隊之後聚集在國會大廈地庫，不少人躺在地上休息。國民警衛隊是應聯邦政府要求，周二傍晚出動，以防國會再次出現混亂場面。他們將24小時輪流看守國會大廈，與國會警察一樣有權拘捕違法人士。到周六會有一萬名國民警衛隊在華盛頓戒備。<br />\n<br />\n議長佩洛西說有共和黨議員拒絕配合安檢，繞過金屬探測器，甚至出言侮辱國會警察，計劃向不合作的議員罰款，從議員薪金扣取五千美元，再犯扣一萬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190206/1de9c2b03488465e87791b9fe84bfa31.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20190206%2F1de9c2b03488465e87791b9fe84bfa31.gif&h=e3e2e5d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下周就是總統就職典禮，現場一帶已守衛森嚴，訂房網站Airbnb亦取消未來一周華盛頓市區的住宿預約。<br />\n<br />\n但據報當局仍然憂慮當天會有極端分子示威，計劃增加警衛隊規模至二萬人。國防部仍在與特勤局商討最終部署，當局會每天向拜登團隊匯報。<br />\n<br />\n至於拜登確認會按照傳統，在典禮前一晚留宿近200年歷史的布萊爾國賓館。這裡與白宮僅一街之隔，歷來接待過眾多國家元首、政要名人。<br />\n<br />\n而就職禮當晚的傳統舞會就因應疫情取消，改為電視直播節目，將包含正副總統發言。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_5xzmNeDRHQ&amp;ab_channel=%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96CABLETV%26%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9ECABLENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_5xzmNeDRHQ%26ab_channel%3D%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B7%259A%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596CABLETV%2526%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B7%259A%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259ECABLENews&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=2120d98e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_5xzmNeDRHQ&amp;ab_channel=%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96CABLETV%26%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9ECABLENews</a>"},{"pid":"85b15153c03f7b9d39f980f42a6f93f27581b69d","tid":2368403,"uid":256837,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T07:01:57.000Z","msg":"佩洛西仲欽點咗個有中國女spy honey trap醜聞嘅眾議員做彈劾主任同國土安全部㖭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70ab3ea83e120929702a48bb7e6d4de2f61a81b","tid":2368403,"uid":58335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T07:06:43.000Z","msg":"佩洛閪變左大口狗?"},{"pid":"c747f98fe12e19f8bed4862c17113c767ec6ae6c","tid":2368403,"uid":273059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T07:08:18.000Z","msg":"共產"},{"pid":"a5447628683451dbfcbc3dd1022fdff7ae4fb4e8","tid":2368403,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T07:11:40.000Z","msg":"美國民建聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da150aa0f21da19e8e7a3c484619a1c220cb5a32","tid":2368403,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85b15153c03f7b9d39f980f42a6f93f27581b69d","tid":2368403,"uid":256837,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T07:01:57.000Z","msg":"佩洛西仲欽點咗個有中國女spy honey trap醜聞嘅眾議員做彈劾主任同國土安全部㖭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T07:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c3207cebbfbca413ecb3e88012a4b13edf9f0e","tid":2368403,"uid":2607,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T07:15:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑撚死我 乜撚野契媽呀你班友係咁捧"},{"pid":